== Firmware ==
== External Hardware == 
  * 10BaseT Ethernet port (RJ-45)
  * Centronics/Parallel printer port
  * Server Test button
  * 9-35 VDC mains adapter socket

== Compatible Mains Adapters (Non-HP) ==
  * Panasonic AC Adapter model  [http://www.amazon.co.jp/%E3%83%91%E3%83%8A%E3%82%BD%E3%83%8B%E3%83%83%E3%82%AF-Panasonic-%E3%83%8A%E3%83%8E%E3%82%A4%E3%83%BC%E7%99%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%A9%9F%E7%94%A8AC%E3%82%A2%E3%83%80%E3%83%97%E3%82%BF%E3%83%BC-%E3%83%96%E3%83%A9%E3%83%83%E3%82%AF-FFJ9140002/dp/B008H0FFK0 FFJ9140002] (Input voltage: 100V @ ~50/60Hz; Output voltage: 13.5V @ 0.8A) - supplied with Japanese Domestic Market "NanoE" humidifiers

== Supported Protocols ==
  * IPv4 
  * Novell IPX
  * SNMP via Java-based configuration utility
  * HTTP
  * [http://h30499.www3.hp.com/t5/Black-and-White/What-is-DLC-LLC/td-p/4846949#.Uq86Cjz5OtU IBM DLC/LLC]
  * DHCP/BootP
  * Telnet
